<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>보험 DB 사이트</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="hero">
      <div class="topbar">
        <span class="badge">보험 정보 제공형 랜딩</span>
        <span class="sub-badge">설계사 연결 서비스</span>
      </div>
      <h1>보험료가 부담되시나요?</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">현재 가입된 보험 상태를 확인하고 전문 보험설계사 상담 연결을 받아보세요.</p>
      <div class="cta-group">
        <a href="#consult" class="cta">상담 신청하기</a>
        <a href="#consult" class="cta">보험 점검 요청</a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section>
      <h2>이런 분들에게 추천드립니다</h2>
      <ul class="recommend-list">
        <li>보험료가 너무 많이 나가는 것 같은 분</li>
        <li>내가 어떤 보험에 가입했는지 잘 모르는 분</li>
        <li>보험 점검 상담이 필요한 분</li>
        <li>실비/특약 확인이 필요한 분</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="feature-grid">
      <h2>어떻게 진행되나요?</h2>
      <div class="flow">
        <article class="feature">
          <h3>1. 간단 설문 작성</h3>
          <p>현재 보험 상황을 간단하게 입력해주세요.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="feature">
          <h3>2. 전문 설계사 연결</h3>
          <p>입력 정보를 바탕으로 상담 가능한 설계사를 연결해드립니다.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="feature">
          <h3>3. 상담 진행</h3>
          <p>보험 분석 및 상담은 전문 자격 보험설계사가 진행합니다.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="consult" class="consult">
      <h2>보험 점검 상담 신청</h2>
      <% if (success) { %>
      <p class="success">상담 요청이 접수되었습니다. 빠르게 연락드리겠습니다.</p>
      <% } %>
      <% if (fail === "agreement") { %>
      <p class="error">동의 항목을 모두 체크해야 상담 신청이 가능합니다.</p>
      <% } %>
      <% if (fail === "validation") { %>
      <p class="error">
        입력값을 다시 확인해주세요. (이름/연락처/지역/월 예산/상담 가능 시간/원하는 보장/기존 보험/연령대/성별/최근 점검)
      </p>
      <% } %>
      <% if (fail === "csrf") { %>
      <p class="error">보안 토큰이 만료되었습니다. 다시 제출해주세요.</p>
      <% } %>
      <form action="/consult" method="POST" class="consult-form">
        <input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="<%= csrfToken %>" />
        <div class="field-group">
          <span class="field-label">상담 희망 여부</span>
          <div class="choice-chips choice-chips--2">
            <label class="chip"
              ><input type="radio" name="consultHope" value="yes" checked /><span>희망</span></label
            >
            <label class="chip"
              ><input type="radio" name="consultHope" value="no" /><span>미희망</span></label
            >
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="field-group field-group--text">
          <label class="field-label" for="applicant-available-time">상담 가능 시간</label>
          <select id="applicant-available-time" name="availableTime" required>
            <option value="" selected disabled>상담 가능 시간 선택</option>
            <option value="morning">오전 (09:00~12:00)</option>
            <option value="afternoon">오후 (12:00~18:00)</option>
            <option value="evening">저녁 (18:00~21:00)</option>
            <option value="anytime">상관없음</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div class="field-group field-group--text">
          <label class="field-label" for="applicant-phone">연락처</label>
          <input
            id="applicant-phone"
            name="phone"
            type="tel"
            inputmode="numeric"
            autocomplete="tel"
            placeholder="01012345678"
            required
          />
        </div>
        <div class="field-group field-group--text">
          <label class="field-label" for="applicant-name">이름</label>
          <input id="applicant-name" name="name" placeholder="이름을 입력해주세요" required />
        </div>
        <div class="field-group field-group--text">
          <label class="field-label" for="applicant-budget">월 예산</label>
          <select id="applicant-budget" name="monthlyBudget" required>
            <option value="" selected disabled>월 예산 선택</option>
            <option value="200">200만원</option>
            <option value="300">300만원</option>
            <option value="400">400만원</option>
            <option value="500">500만원</option>
            <option value="600">600만원</option>
            <option value="700">700만원</option>
            <option value="800">800만원</option>
            <option value="900">900만원</option>
            <option value="1000plus">1000만원+</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div class="field-group field-group--text">
          <label class="field-label" for="applicant-coverage">원하는 보장</label>
          <select id="applicant-coverage" name="desiredCoverage" required>
            <option value="" selected disabled>원하는 보장 선택</option>
            <option value="life">생명보험</option>
            <option value="nonlife">손해보험</option>
            <option value="third">제3보험</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div class="field-group">
          <span class="field-label">현재 보험 가입 여부</span>
          <div class="choice-chips choice-chips--insured">
            <label class="chip"
              ><input type="radio" name="insuredStatus" value="yes" checked /><span>있다</span></label
            >
            <label class="chip"
              ><input type="radio" name="insuredStatus" value="no" /><span>없다</span></label
            >
            <label class="chip"
              ><input type="radio" name="insuredStatus" value="unknown" /><span>잘 모르겠다</span></label
            >
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="field-group" id="existing-insurance-group">
          <span class="field-label">기존 보험 (중복 선택 가능)</span>
          <label class="check-item">
            <input type="checkbox" name="existingInsurance" value="life" />
            생명보험
          </label>
          <label class="check-item">
            <input type="checkbox" name="existingInsurance" value="nonlife" />
            손해보험
          </label>
          <label class="check-item">
            <input type="checkbox" name="existingInsurance" value="third" />
            제3보험
          </label>
          <label class="check-item">
            <input type="checkbox" name="existingInsurance" value="unknown" />
            잘 모르겠다
          </label>
        </div>
        <div class="field-group">
          <span class="field-label">최근 보험 점검 경험</span>
          <div class="choice-chips choice-chips--check">
            <label class="chip"
              ><input type="radio" name="lastInsuranceCheck" value="within3m" required /><span
                >3개월 이내</span
              ></label
            >
            <label class="chip"
              ><input type="radio" name="lastInsuranceCheck" value="within6m" /><span>6개월 이내</span></label
            >
            <label class="chip"
              ><input type="radio" name="lastInsuranceCheck" value="within1y" /><span>1년 이내</span></label
            >
            <label class="chip"
              ><input type="radio" name="lastInsuranceCheck" value="over1y" /><span>1년 이상</span></label
            >
            <label class="chip"
              ><input type="radio" name="lastInsuranceCheck" value="unknown" /><span>기억 안 남</span></label
            >
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="field-group field-group--text">
          <label class="field-label" for="applicant-region">지역</label>
          <select id="applicant-region" name="region" required>
            <option value="" selected disabled>지역 선택</option>
            <option value="chungbuk">충청북도</option>
            <option value="chungnam">충청남도</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div class="field-group">
          <span class="field-label">연령대</span>
          <div class="choice-chips choice-chips--age">
            <label class="chip"
              ><input type="radio" name="ageBand" value="20" required /><span>20대</span></label
            >
            <label class="chip"
              ><input type="radio" name="ageBand" value="30" /><span>30대</span></label
            >
            <label class="chip"
              ><input type="radio" name="ageBand" value="40" /><span>40대</span></label
            >
            <label class="chip"
              ><input type="radio" name="ageBand" value="50" /><span>50대</span></label
            >
            <label class="chip"
              ><input type="radio" name="ageBand" value="60" /><span>60대 이상</span></label
            >
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="field-group">
          <span class="field-label">성별</span>
          <div class="choice-chips choice-chips--2">
            <label class="chip"
              ><input type="radio" name="gender" value="male" required /><span>남</span></label
            >
            <label class="chip"
              ><input type="radio" name="gender" value="female" /><span>여</span></label
            >
          </div>
        </div>
        <label class="check-item">
          <input type="checkbox" name="agreePrivacy" required />
          개인정보 수집 및 이용 동의
        </label>
        <label class="check-item">
          <input type="checkbox" name="agreeThirdParty" required />
          보험 상담 진행을 위한 제3자 제공 동의
        </label>
        <label class="check-item">
          <input type="checkbox" name="agreeContact" required />
          상담 연결 및 연락 수신 동의
        </label>
        <button type="submit">상담 요청 보내기</button>
      </form>
      <p class="notice">
        ※ 본 서비스는 보험 상담 연결 플랫폼입니다.<br />
        ※ 실제 보험 상담 및 계약은 전문 보험설계사를 통해 진행됩니다.<br />
        ※ 개인 상황에 따라 상담 내용은 달라질 수 있습니다.
      </p>
    </section>
    <script>
      (function () {
        const statusInputs = document.querySelectorAll('input[name="insuredStatus"]');
        const group = document.getElementById("existing-insurance-group");
        const checkboxes = group ? group.querySelectorAll('input[name="existingInsurance"]') : [];
        if (!group || statusInputs.length === 0) return;

        const syncVisibility = () => {
          const selected = document.querySelector('input[name="insuredStatus"]:checked');
          const show = selected && selected.value === "yes";
          group.style.display = show ? "block" : "none";
          if (!show) {
            checkboxes.forEach((el) => {
              el.checked = false;
            });
          }
        };

        const syncUnknownRule = (event) => {
          const target = event.target;
          if (!target || target.name !== "existingInsurance") return;
          if (target.value === "unknown" && target.checked) {
            checkboxes.forEach((el) => {
              if (el.value !== "unknown") el.checked = false;
            });
          } else if (target.value !== "unknown" && target.checked) {
            const unknown = group.querySelector('input[name="existingInsurance"][value="unknown"]');
            if (unknown) unknown.checked = false;
          }
        };

        statusInputs.forEach((el) => el.addEventListener("change", syncVisibility));
        checkboxes.forEach((el) => el.addEventListener("change", syncUnknownRule));
        syncVisibility();
      })();
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
